JobsCentral Singapore Jobs - Urgent Requirement of Part Time F&B Banquet Service Crew by Jobs Exchange Pte Ltd
Jobs Exchange Pte Ltd
Our company, Jobs Exchange Pte Ltd established to provide Just-In-Time Event Management Service & solutions to the staffing problems faced by the Hospitality Industry in Singapore. Our competitive edge lies in our ability to deploy large number of staff (both full-time and part-time) to meet our clients’ manpower needs within a short period of time. The primary function of the the company is to recruit and deploy hospitality personnel to 5- or 6-star Hotels to perform all service functions, ranging from banquet service,  restaurant hostess, kitchen helper, steward, as well as bartender and banquet manager.
Closing Date: 30th May 201430/04/2014
Urgent Requirement of Part Time F&B; Banquet Service Crew
Part Time F&B; Banquet Service staff
We are urgently looking for Young, Energetic, Outgoing, Hardworking & Articulate Individuals who are passionate about being in service industries. Join us for a Life Long learning experience and brong your friends along !!!
Job Function - Responsible for serving, clearing, taking orders, table setting and perform housekeeping at the F&B; outlets.
To provide excellent F&B; service for Big Hall Banquet events @ 5 star hotels , Private events , Branded Restaurants, Catering Events outside Hotel’s premises etc etc ...
GOOD TO HAVE - Presentable; Charismatic personality; Attentive with good customer service attitude;
Pleasant disposition & enthusiastic; Relevant experience in F&B; is valuable & Dicipline
WORK LOCATION: 5 star Hotels, Restaurants, Country / Social Clubs etc.
Salary : $8 per hour depending on days , Salary will be creditted into your bank account hassle free  on every Tuesday & Friday between 6pm to 11pm  **( for a limited time period, CASH AFTER WORK on 9th , 10th , 11th & 21st of May )**
Requirement -
Must register with Jobs Exchange Pte Ltd in order to work
Relevant experience in F&B; is valuable, On-The-Job-Training , presentable & charismatic personality , customer service oriented, able to commit during weekends , able to do long hours shift ,
16 years old and above ,For foreign student, MUST BE STUDYING in a Government recognized institute with valid student permits ,to  bring along all identification(s) for the interview.
-To contact Ian/Nizam for interviews (Mon-Sat from 1pm - 7pm) Contact Number: 9451 2680/9029 1556  or -SKYPE @ JobsExchange on every Mon – Fri 3pm -6pm or -Send your resumes to
